publisher			Armor Games, Inc.							
publish_time	 Summer 2016		
desc_long							评测						“It's probably my maturity as a gamer but I have a real soft spot for atmospheric adventure games, and Thomas Brush AKA Atmos Games is delivering that in spades with Pinstripe, an adventure, platform, puzzler with artwork 3 years in the making and a look and feel just oozing class.”Indie Retro News“Features a great art style and fantastic soundtrack.”The Initiative Check“Thomas Brush, the creator of Coma and Skinny, has envisioned Orpheus’ descent to Hades with incredible art direction and a soundtrack full of wonder and tension to create an extremely promising product.”Hardcore Gamer												关于这款游戏							Pinstripe is an atmospheric exploration game by Thomas Brush, creator of award winning games Coma and Skinny.Pinstripe is about a man looking for his wife in hell, and plays much like an immersive, interactive story. All art, music, and development has been in development for almost 3 years.Pinstripe was featured at the IndieCade Showcase @ E3 2013.Explore 4 unique worlds in search of your dead wife. Listen to an immersive and unique soundtrack crafted with classical instruments reminiscent of the Zelda franchise.Use your blunderbuss to find your way through bizarre beasts and interesting puzzles.						
title	 Pinstripe			
