desc_short	-----								Pinstripe is an atmospheric puzzle-platformer about a dead guy looking for his wife in Hell. Explore beautifully designed landscapes, solve interesting puzzles, and enjoy a unique soundtrack crafted with classical instruments and bizarre soundscapes.							
developer									Thomas Brush								
